name: I Am Happy.
description:
There are 2 kinds of people one who have literally everything in this world but still not satisfied with what they have,on the other hand there are those people who have limited things/money but they are still happy and satisfied!
I tried to show this scenario by my art.
This hut embraces the reflection of those satisfied people who are happy in what they have and the buildings behind the hut are those who are still not satisfied .
